Class AeXMLParserSchemaHandler

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
org.xml.sax.ContentHandler, org.xml.sax.DTDHandler, org.xml.sax.EntityResolver, org.xml.sax.ErrorHandler
public class AeXMLParserSchemaHandler
extends AeXMLParserDefaultHandler

This class implements an XML parser default handler. It extends the AE default handler and simply adds the ability to resolve schema entities from a list of schemas. FIXMEQ (Castor SchemaWriter) XML parser schema handler uses Castor Schema objects to resolve schema entities - if we want to remove our dependency on the Castor schema-writer, we need to change this behavior
